ent-Z14ClothingOuterArmorPSZ9D = PSZ-9d "Duty Armor"
    .desc = This early model of the Duty bodysuit is the Spetsnaz PSZ-9 body armor modified for the Zone. The suit is capable of stopping a rifle bullet, however, this level of protection comes at the cost of its weight, bulkiness and virtually non-existent anomaly protection.
    .suffix = Z14

ent-Z14STClothingOuterArmorHeavySera = OP-14 Armored Coveralls (Green)
    .desc = Based on a common jumpsuit, armored because it has increased protection from most physical damage by the armor plates. It also adds weight, but provides excellent projectile protection for combines such as this one.
    .suffix = Z14

ent-Z14STClothingOuterArmorLimaSeraphimStrash = "Sentinel" Armored Suit (Worn)
    .desc = Same as the Sentinel — now in green!
    .suffix = Z14

ent-Z14STClothingOuterArmorSeraphimStrash = "Sentinel" Armored Suit
    .desc = An old, battle-worn bulat suit from Monolith's arsenal, marked by time and fierce combat. Despite its age, it remains a reliable shield in the Zone. Its green camouflage finish gives it a distinctive look.
    .suffix = Z14
